emuInput.TitMainTitle: Members of Lemuel Chapter 16 OES PHA Masons, seated: Mrs. Johnson, Mrs. M. Budd, Mrs. R. Mitchell, Mrs. Z. B. Stevenson, Mrs. H. Gloster, Mrs. E. Patterson, Mrs. J. Thompson, Mrs. S. Taylor; standing: Jefferson Johnson, Sylvester Squaires, Hampton Jeter Jr., and Stonewall Lett, in interior with piano and clock on wall reading 9:35
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1963, pg. 14, reads: "Lemuel Chapter Celebrates - Members of Lemuel Chapter 16 OES PHA, one of the oldest chapters in Deborah Grand Lodge, commemorated the occasion when Patron Stonewall J. Lett became Grand Junior Warden of the State of Pennsylvania recently. Members are left to right, seated, first row: Mmes I. Johnson, M. Budd, R. Mitchell, Z.B. Stevenson, H. Gloster, E. Patterson, H. Thompson and S. Taylor.  Second row: Mmes. B. Crawford, B. Rancies, A. Smith, A.B. Scott, L. Joyner, M.A. Peals, O. Boxley, A. Brown, A. Tucker, and L. Watts.  Masonic leaders standing in rear are Jefferson Johnson, Sylvester Squaires, Hampton Jeter Jr. and Stonewall J. Lett W.P. the celebrant"
